/92b25e20gy1fqb1rd529gj212w0dqtn9.jpg\" /></div>","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"1338","username":"xwr","adminid":"0","groupid":"57","memberstatus":"0","number":"1337","dbdateline":"1544411559","groupiconid":"12"},{"pid":"41892982","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"kepler","authorid":"428624","dateline":"2018-12-10 11:19","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41892766&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">xwr 发表于 2018-12-10 11:04</font></a><br />\n从专楼搬些图过来</div><br />\n这样对比着看，确实利兹人设的纤细感就出来了。<br />\nps，我一直以为利兹版优子头发比tv版短，由过肩变成了及肩，仔细看，头发没短，脖子长了<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/009.gif\" />","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"1339","username":"kepler","adminid":"-1","groupid":"4","memberstatus":"0","number":"1338","dbdateline":"1544411992","groupiconid":null},{"pid":"41893163","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"xwr","authorid":"179647","dateline":"2018-12-10 11:31","message":"双簧管哨片<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nUnderstanding the Oboe ---The United States Army Field Band<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/jNaS_jy3_eI?t=20m2s\">https://youtu.be/jNaS_jy3_eI?t=20m2s</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<div class=\"img\"><img src=\"http://wx4.sinaimg.cn/mw690/dcec95dfly1fr6c2nssscj20u50jdgmt.jpg\" /></div><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n哨片做起来相当麻烦，从选材到制作细节要求都很高，错了的话就根本不能用，即使好用的寿命也只能论天算，那套制作工具似乎也价格不菲，更有意思的是(木制）双簧管本身寿命也有限，一般4-8年，因为会吸收水分，特别是上半部分连接处。<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<br />\r\nWhy would anybody want to play the oboe?<br />\r\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QSAllHtkaa0\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=QSAllHtkaa0</a><br />\r<div class=\"reply_wrap\">The oboe? The Devil's reed? The ill wind that nobody blows good; suffocation on a stick?<br />\r\nWhy wouldn't anyone want to play an instrument that demands total dedication in the construction of a vital component guaranteed to fail almost as soon as you finish shaping it, if it's even usable once it's first finished?<br />\r\nAn instrument where an inadequate student's instrument costs more than some lower level professional grade clarinets and a few used cars?<br />\r\nBecause I love the sound of an oboe, and if I could afford one I'd buy one. Nothing else sounds even close to an oboe.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n双簧管？魔鬼的哨片？这不算是绝对的坏事，（好事是）在一根棍子上窒息么？<br />\r\n为什么会有人想演奏这么一种乐器，它要求绝对专注来制作一个即便刚刚完成时能用，但几乎在制作完成时就保证会完蛋的关键部件？<br />\r\n一种乐器，学生用劣质货竟然比低专业级的单簧管和某些二手车还贵？<br />\r\n因为我热爱双簧管的声音，如果我能买得起我会买一支。没有任何其他的声音可以和双簧管相提并论。</div><br />\n","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"1340","username":"xwr","adminid":"0","groupid":"57","memberstatus":"0","number":"1339","dbdateline":"1544412709","groupiconid":"12"},{"pid":"41893256","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"yone0000","authorid":"154038","dateline":"2018-12-10 11:38","message":"这套人设对单马尾的相性非常好，夏纪和希美一套上去马上变池了<img src=\"https://static.saraba1st.com/image/smiley/face2017/068.png\" />","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"1341","username":"yone0000","adminid":"0","groupid":"54","memberstatus":"0","number":"1340","dbdateline":"1544413131","groupiconid":"13"},{"pid":"41893342","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"扶扶老奶奶","authorid":"459217","dateline":"2018-12-10 11:44","message":"<div class=\"reply_wrap\"><a href=\"https://bbs.saraba1st.com/2b/forum.php?mod=redirect&amp;goto=findpost&amp;pid=41892982&amp;ptid=1795203\"><font color=\"#999999\">kepler 发表于 2018-12-10 11:19</font></a><br />\r\n这样对比着看，确实利兹人设的纤细感就出来了。<br />\r\nps，我一直以为利兹版优子头发比tv版短，由过肩变成了及 ...</div><br />\n优子三年级确实把头发剪短了一些，可以参考新剧场版人设","anonymous":"0","attachment":"0","status":"0","replycredit":"0","position":"1342","username":"扶扶老奶奶","adminid":"0","groupid":"32","memberstatus":"0","number":"1341","dbdateline":"1544413465","groupiconid":"8"},{"pid":"41893406","tid":"1795203","first":"0","author":"百响","authorid":"421463","dateline"